This src/ directory contains all C++ and CUDA source code for the PSCF 
package.  Each of the subdirectories util/, pscf/, prdc/, r1d/, rpc/, and 
rpg/ contain source code from a particular C++ namespace.  Subdirectories 
util/ and test/ are maintained as separate github repositories that are 
installed as submodules of the pscfpp respository. 

Subdirectories (corresponding namespace names in parentheses):

  util/  general utilities for scientific computation (Util)
  pscf/  shared classes for entire package PSCF (Pscf)
  prdc/  shared classes for periodic structures (Pscf::Prdc)
  r1d/   real fields, one-dimensional SCFT (Pscf::R1d)
  rpc/   real periodic fields, SCFT & FTS on CPU (Pscf::Rpc)
  rpg/   real periodic fields, SCFT & FTMC on GPU (Pscf::Rpg)
  test/  unit testing framework (base classes)

Files (in repository):

  setopts  - script for managing compile-time options
  makefile - main makefile for in-source compilation (build in src/)
  programs.mod - doxygen page for program command-line interfaces
  CONTENTS - this file

Files (installed by configure script):

  config.mk - main configuration file (editable)

